{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-tsx","path":"/blog/2019/09/announcing-gatsby-plugin-social-cards","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://andri.dk","title":"andri.dk","description":"I make websites, create apps, manage infrastructure, develop products and more.","social":{"twitter":"andrioid"}}},"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Ever seen those images shown next to posts on Twitter, Slack or Facebook? Ever wonder where they come from? Me too!</p>\n<p>This plugin will create automatic cards for your (ReMark) at build-time.</p>\n<h2 id=\"announcing\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#announcing\" aria-label=\"announcing permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Announcing</h2>\n<p>I am ready to announce my new Gatsby plugin, gatsby-plugin-social-cards.</p>\n<p>There are a few alternatives for Gatsby social-cards, but I wanted to try making these cards with SVG, React and the Sharp library that most Gatsby sites already depend on.</p>\n<p>Currently this plugin resides within my site, but if there is interest in it, I'll move it into its own repo. Contact me on Twitter if you have any issues.</p>\n<h2 id=\"features\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#features\" aria-label=\"features permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Features</h2>\n<h3 id=\"backgrounds\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#backgrounds\" aria-label=\"backgrounds permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Backgrounds</h3>\n<p>You can put a cover frontmatter on your post, and we'll use that. Otherwise, we'll use a default-background that you can specify or if that fails, we'll use a fallback one.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 896px; max-width: 896px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/34221344967eb655433086323a4b2d01/e5166/default-design.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"default card design\"\n        title=\"default card design\"\n        src=\"/static/34221344967eb655433086323a4b2d01/ac4a7/default-design.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/34221344967eb655433086323a4b2d01/2bad8/default-design.jpg 224w,\n/static/34221344967eb655433086323a4b2d01/fb05c/default-design.jpg 448w,\n/static/34221344967eb655433086323a4b2d01/ac4a7/default-design.jpg 896w,\n/static/34221344967eb655433086323a4b2d01/e5166/default-design.jpg 1200w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 896px) 100vw, 896px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"designs\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#designs\" aria-label=\"designs permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Designs</h3>\n<p>There are two design available now, \"card\" and \"default\". But we can expand that later.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 896px; max-width: 896px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7987758a52d337e319646b91587e15c4/e5166/card-design.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"default card design\"\n        title=\"default card design\"\n        src=\"/static/7987758a52d337e319646b91587e15c4/ac4a7/card-design.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7987758a52d337e319646b91587e15c4/2bad8/card-design.jpg 224w,\n/static/7987758a52d337e319646b91587e15c4/fb05c/card-design.jpg 448w,\n/static/7987758a52d337e319646b91587e15c4/ac4a7/card-design.jpg 896w,\n/static/7987758a52d337e319646b91587e15c4/e5166/card-design.jpg 1200w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 896px) 100vw, 896px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"author-image\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#author-image\" aria-label=\"author image permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Author image</h3>\n<p>If specified, an author image is shown on the image. That is also configurable.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 896px; max-width: 896px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ac9793437536b1aee7d53ef2f3a1801b/e5166/cover-custom-author.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"default card design\"\n        title=\"default card design\"\n        src=\"/static/ac9793437536b1aee7d53ef2f3a1801b/ac4a7/cover-custom-author.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ac9793437536b1aee7d53ef2f3a1801b/2bad8/cover-custom-author.jpg 224w,\n/static/ac9793437536b1aee7d53ef2f3a1801b/fb05c/cover-custom-author.jpg 448w,\n/static/ac9793437536b1aee7d53ef2f3a1801b/ac4a7/cover-custom-author.jpg 896w,\n/static/ac9793437536b1aee7d53ef2f3a1801b/e5166/cover-custom-author.jpg 1200w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 896px) 100vw, 896px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"custom-author-image\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#custom-author-image\" aria-label=\"custom author image permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Custom author-image</h3>\n<p>The author image can be ommitted if it's not wanted, or customized in the configuration.</p>\n<h2 id=\"install\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#install\" aria-label=\"install permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Install</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"command-line-prompt\"><span data-user=groot data-host=localhost></span><span data-user=groot data-host=localhost></span></span><span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> <span class=\"token function\">add</span> gatsby-plugin-social-cards\r\n<span class=\"token comment\"># or npm install --save gatsby-plugin-social-cards</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-use\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#how-to-use\" aria-label=\"how to use permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How to use</h2>\n<p>Please see the <a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/gatsby-plugin-social-cards\">README</a> for how to use.</p>","excerpt":"Ever seen those images shown next to posts on Twitter, Slack or Facebook? Ever wonder where they come from? Me too! This plugin will create automatic cards for your (ReMark) at build-time. Announcing I am ready to announce my new Gatsby pluginâ€¦","fields":{"title":"Announcing gatsby-plugin-social-cards","date":"2019-09-15T00:00:00.000Z","tags":["react","gatsbyjs","open-graph"],"slug":"/blog/2019/09/announcing-gatsby-plugin-social-cards","socialcard":"gatsby-plugin-social-card/e83e7de0-5c71-5a80-a749-7af5df4458be.jpg"},"frontmatter":{"date":"September 15, 2019","cover":null}}},"pageContex